VERSION=X1

[COMMENT sphere_skillmenu]
SphereServer has a number of hardcoded skillmenu's, this file contains the softcoded component.
The purpose of these specific skillmenus is as follows:
sm_tailor_leather		= Triggered by DClicking a sewing kit and using it on leather
sm_tailor_cloth			= Triggered by DClicking a sewing kit and using it on cloth

[SKILLMENU sm_tailor_leather]
Leather

ON=i_BOOTS_CALF Footwear
SKILLMENU=sm_leather_footwear

ON=i_LEATHER_TUNIC Leather Armour
SKILLMENU=sm_leather_armor

ON=i_STUDDED_TUNIC Studded Armour
SKILLMENU=sm_leather_studded_armor

ON=i_ARMOR_FEMALE_BUSTIER Female Armour
SKILLMENU=sm_leather_female_armor

ON=i_BACKPACK Misc
SKILLMENU=sm_leather_misc

//ON=i_mask_blue Masks
//SKILLMENU=sm_leather_masks

